with expected_protocol(ik.hp.HP6624a, ['ISET? 1', 'ISET? 2', 'ISET? 3',
    'ISET? 4', 'ISET 1,{:.1f}'.format(5), 'ISET 2,{:.1f}'.format(5),
    'ISET 3,{:.1f}'.format(5), 'ISET 4,{:.1f}'.format(5), 'ISET 1,{:.1f}'.
    format(1), 'ISET 2,{:.1f}'.format(2), 'ISET 3,{:.1f}'.format(3),
    'ISET 4,{:.1f}'.format(4)], ['2', '3', '4', '5'], sep='\n') as hp:
    assert sorted(hp.current) == sorted((2, 3, 4, 5) * u.A)
    hp.current = 5 * u.A
    hp.current = 1 * u.A, 2 * u.A, 3 * u.A, 4 * u.A
